 href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/ >Insights</a></li><li class=col-auto><a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/all/best-practices/ class=people-analytics>Best Practices</a></li></ul><div class=blog_box_image> <a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/best-practices/headcount-planning-guide-cfo/ > <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/productive-performance-reviews-in-line-image-686x366.jpg alt="CFO Edition: How to Confidently Approach Your Headcount Planning" data-no-retina> </a></div><h3><a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/best-practices/headcount-planning-guide-cfo/ >CFO Edition: How to Confidently Approach Your Headcount Planning</a></h3> Headcount planning is absolutely critical to get right, and CFOs play an essential role in the process. Download the guide to discover how CFOs can support strategic headcount planning.</div></div><div class="resource-single col-md-6 col-lg-4"><div class=blog_box><ul class="blog_tags row no-gutters"><li class=col-auto><a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/ >Insights</a></li><li class=col-auto><a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/all/best-practices/ class=people-analytics>Best Practices</a></li></ul><div class=blog_box_image> <a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/best-practices/headcount-planning-guide/ > <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/topimage1-686x366.png alt="How to Confidently Approach Your Headcount Planning" data-no-retina> </a></div><h3><a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/insights/best-practices/headcount-planning-guide/ >How to Confidently Approach Your Headcount Planning</a></h3> Effective headcount planning can drive faster growth, greater innovation, and promote a better employee experience that leads to increased retention. Download the guide to discover how you can achieve these results for 